label: Scarsdale Inquirer
title: Scarsdale_Inquirer
exrest: Scarsdale Inquirer is a local newspaper that was founded in 1901 as a weekly. The first issue was dated July 4, 1901. Their weekly print edition is published on Fridays; the paper's website's daily e-Edition is self-described as "365 days."
